dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents tax parcels for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2010. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Milwaukee_Parcels_2010.gdb.
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use.Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit: http://gis-mclio.opendata.arcgis.com/
